-- Mauritius’s Phoenix Beverages Rises to Highest in 7 Weeks
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-03-02T07:04:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-02/mauritius-s-phoenix-beverages-rises-to-highest-in-7-weeks.html
Mauritius’s  Phoenix Beverages Ltd. (PBL) ,
the country’s largest brewer and soft drinks bottler, surged to
its highest level in more than seven weeks.  The stock gained 4 percent to 208 rupees by 10:43 a.m., in
 Port Louis , the capital, its strongest level since Jan. 18,
according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
